OL,3,CCan the UK's first drug consumption
OL,4,Croom reduce Scotland's drug-related
OL,5,Cdeaths?
OL,7,FThose attending the drug consumption
OL,8,Froom, called The Thistle, will be able
OL,9,Fto access clean needles and inject
OL,10,Fwith NHS staff on hand, ITV News
OL,11,FCorrespondent Peter Smith reports
OL,13,FScotland is now four years into what
OL,14,Fthen-First Minister Nicola Sturgeon
OL,15,Fcalled a drug deaths public health
OL,16,Femergency.
OL,18,FAlmost 5,000 people have died in that
OL,19,Ftime.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
