OL,3,CCan the UK's first drug consumption
OL,4,Croom reduce Scotland's drug-related
OL,5,Cdeaths?
OL,7,FThe annual figure just increased
OL,8,Fagain, and Glasgow saw the sharpest
OL,9,Fincrease, with 25% more deaths due to
OL,10,Fdrugs.
OL,12,FIn fact, Glasgow is the drug death
OL,13,Fcapital of Europe.
OL,15,FBut the city is about to experiment
OL,16,Fwith one possible answer.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
