OL,3,CCan the UK's first drug consumption
OL,4,Croom reduce Scotland's drug-related
OL,5,Cdeaths?
OL,7,FOn Monday, a drug consumption room
OL,8,Fwill be opened - the first place in
OL,9,Fthe UK where people will not only be
OL,10,Fallowed but actively encouraged, to
OL,11,Ftake their drugs without fear of
OL,12,Farrest.
OL,14,FBuying, selling, and possessing drugs
OL,15,Fis still going to be illegal in
OL,16,FScotland.
OL,18,FBut as of next week, all users in
OL,19,FGlasgow will get a free pass as long
OL,20,Fas they're taking their drugs inside
OL,21,Fthe clinic at The Thistle.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
