OL,3,CCan the UK's first drug consumption
OL,4,Croom reduce Scotland's drug-related
OL,5,Cdeaths?
OL,7,FThey will be able to access clean
OL,8,Fneedles and inject with NHS staff on
OL,9,Fhand to respond to any overdoses.
OL,11,FIt is also about engagement with those
OL,12,Fwho are often at the fringes of
OL,13,Fsociety: hidden away, injecting in
OL,14,Falleyways and the backstairs of public
OL,15,Fcar parks.
OL,17,FMany are homeless, struggling with
OL,18,Fmental health issues and self-
OL,19,Fmedicating.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
