OL,3,CCan the UK's first drug consumption
OL,4,Croom reduce Scotland's drug-related
OL,5,Cdeaths?
OL,7,FThey are not easy to reach and some
OL,8,Fhave had little, if any, contact with
OL,9,Fhealth professionals, such as dentists
OL,10,For a GP, which leads to other health
OL,11,Fcomplications in their lives.
OL,13,FThese kinds of drug consumption rooms
OL,14,Fare already operational in Canada,
OL,15,FAustralia, and across Europe.
OL,17,FWe've seen the impact for ourselves at
OL,18,Fthis clinic in Denmark.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
