OL,3,CCan the UK's first drug consumption
OL,4,Croom reduce Scotland's drug-related
OL,5,Cdeaths?
OL,7,FSince it opened more than a decade
OL,8,Fago, needle sharing was almost
OL,9,Feradicated, and the Danish HIV rate
OL,10,Fplummeted to one of the lowest in the
OL,11,Fworld.
OL,13,FContrast that with the picture in
OL,14,FGlasgow city centre - where there's
OL,15,Fbeen an HIV outbreak among drug users,
OL,16,Fand used needles are being discarded
OL,17,Fin public places.
OL,19,FHowever, part of the effectiveness in
OL,20,Fother countries is the entire holistic
OL,21,Fpackage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
