OL,3,CCan the UK's first drug consumption
OL,4,Croom reduce Scotland's drug-related
OL,5,Cdeaths?
OL,7,FIf someone is in need of mental health
OL,8,Fsupport, it can be arranged.
OL,10,FIn Scotland, if they are identified as
OL,11,Fneeding mental health support, there
OL,12,Fis a lengthy waiting list for access.
OL,14,FThe same goes for access to
OL,15,Frehabilitation beds for anyone trying
OL,16,Fto come off drugs: Scotland just
OL,17,Fdoesn't have enough.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
