OL,3,CCan the UK's first drug consumption
OL,4,Croom reduce Scotland's drug-related
OL,5,Cdeaths?
OL,7,FHe ought to be the exact demographic
OL,8,Fthe drug consumption room would be
OL,9,Fexpected to target, but the location
OL,10,Fof the clinic at the edge of Glasgow
OL,11,Fcity centre is a problem for him.
OL,13,F"I can't see myself personally going
OL,14,Fin there, no," he said.
OL,16,F"You want to take your drugs as soon
OL,17,Fas you get them. That's what I'm
OL,18,Fsaying. You won't come all the way up
OL,19,Fhere once you've scored in the city
OL,20,Fcentre, and want to use in the
OL,21,Fconsumption room."
