OL,3,CCan the UK's first drug consumption
OL,4,Croom reduce Scotland's drug-related
OL,5,Cdeaths?
OL,7,FThis initial scepticism in Scotland
OL,8,Fwill be a challenge, but drug
OL,9,Fconsumption rooms are already
OL,10,Feffective around the world.
OL,12,FUntil now, though, drug consumption
OL,13,Frooms have been blocked from opening
OL,14,Fin the UK by Westminster.
OL,16,FThe relevant legislation - the Misuse
OL,17,Fof Drugs Act - is not devolved, but
OL,18,Fthe Scottish government fought hard to
OL,19,Fget this pioneering clinic open, and
OL,20,Fthey believe it will make a difference
OL,21,Fin drug-related deaths and harm.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
