OL,3,CCan the UK's first drug consumption
OL,4,Croom reduce Scotland's drug-related
OL,5,Cdeaths?
OL,7,FBut even when it opens, there are
OL,8,Fstill legal contradictions and
OL,9,Fcomplications.
OL,11,FAnyone taking drugs inside The Thistle
OL,12,Fhas effectively been given immunity
OL,13,Ffrom prosecution for drug possession.
OL,15,FHowever, in order to obtain drugs,
OL,16,Fthey have to buy them. But buying
OL,17,Fdrugs from dealers is illegal. And
OL,18,Feven then being in possession of drugs
OL,19,Fto carry them to the clinic will still
OL,20,Fbe illegal.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
