OL,3,CCan the UK's first drug consumption
OL,4,Croom reduce Scotland's drug-related
OL,5,Cdeaths?
OL,7,FThese are issues that need to be
OL,8,Fironed out, and there is an
OL,9,Funderstanding Police Scotland will
OL,10,Fhave a "common sense approach" to
OL,11,Fpeople using the clinic.
OL,13,FHowever, there is a risk to the local
OL,14,Fcommunity that this clinic could
OL,15,Fcreate an isolated drug ghetto within
OL,16,FGlasgow.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
