OL,3,CCan the UK's first drug consumption
OL,4,Croom reduce Scotland's drug-related
OL,5,Cdeaths?
OL,7,FPolice cannot ignore open drug deals
OL,8,Fif pushers start hanging around
OL,9,Foutside the service targeting people
OL,10,Fgoing in and coming out. But if there
OL,11,Fis any kind of police presence, that
OL,12,Fcould deter people from using the
OL,13,Fservice at all.
OL,15,FIt is just a three-year pilot, for now.
OL,17,FIn that time, all eyes will be on
OL,18,FGlasgow to see what difference it
OL,19,Fmakes to the drug deaths and the lives
OL,20,Fof the most at-risk people like Billy.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
